item.title: Teleport help
item.dc:creator: @deadlyhorror deadlyhorror
item.description:
@deadlyhorror wrote:

pk4agirl:

im using deathlypvpz and i just added some new bosses customs and i want to add them in the boss teleport section in tele book so they can click on that to teleport to there how i can do that?

Not positive but doesn’t seem too hard, what you need is in clickingbuttons.java, find the list of bosses and then add a case for the tele with the coords. Sorry if I’m no help. If you can’t get it then just think about adding a tele command instead. That’s so much easier lol
